{"tid":395830,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"水波爐","createTime":"2017-09-11T07:11:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-11T13:23:02.000Z","uid":34409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f5a025076d2a9baff8d4e5c105c0cf86c3aefc55","tid":395830,"uid":34409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T07:11:12.000Z","msg":"因為黎緊想買部水波爐返屋企用，咁係我做功課睇下買乜牌子較好時，<br />\n我見到呢個網站咁講：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://ksk.tw/blog/post/296266756-%5Bsharp%E5%A4%8F%E6%99%AE%5D-ax-xp100%E6%B0%B4%E6%B3%A2%E7%88%90~%E9%96%8B%E7%AE%B1%E5%88%86%E4%BA%AB%E8%88%87%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fksk.tw%2Fblog%2Fpost%2F296266756-%255Bsharp%25E5%25A4%258F%25E6%2599%25AE%255D-ax-xp100%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E6%25B3%25A2%25E7%2588%2590~%25E9%2596%258B%25E7%25AE%25B1%25E5%2588%2586%25E4%25BA%25AB%25E8%2588%2587%25E5%259F%25BA%25E6%259C%25AC%25E6%2593%258D%25E4%25BD%259C&d=zm1YLSEXK%2Bh7fiA9yBSUQdU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=166db271\" target=\"_blank\">http://ksk.tw/blog/post/296266756-%5Bsharp%E5%A4%8F%E6%99%AE%5D-ax-xp100%E6%B0%B4%E6%B3%A2%E7%88%90~%E9%96%8B%E7%AE%B1%E5%88%86%E4%BA%AB%E8%88%87%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C</a><br />\n<br />\n日本常看到水波爐的品牌，就SHARP、日立Hitachi、TOSHIBA、PANASONIC等。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">在這些品牌裡面的水波爐，只有SHARP可以真正全程沒有使用到微波(可單純烤或單純蒸)，<br />\n其他品牌的水波爐在烹調的過程裡面都可能會偷用微波來輔助。</span><br />\n<br />\n篇野睇返日期期實都兩年前，我想問今時今日咁多牌子既水波爐當中，<br />\n係咪仲係只有Sharp係咁？<br />\n<br />\n同埋各位師兄用緊乜野水波爐可以推薦呀？"},{"pid":"8e6160142c1eb9611c46d10154e813e2ecc24b34","tid":395830,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T07:12:42.000Z","msg":"其實技術唔太純熟 建議唔買....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca9622a2a55cb7255cd0a528689305ffc44b7dbf","tid":395830,"uid":34409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T07:16:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實技術唔太純熟 建議唔買....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n出左兩三年都仲未純熟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa8f4d17cc069a6eaebdb007eefa0f98216b758c","tid":395830,"uid":49316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T13:23:02.000Z","msg":"用緊東芝430。 個super steam mode 唔用微波。蒸魚同蛋要多D時間。焗同烤好得。<br />\n<br />\n惠而普都有出。無用過  好似有漏水問題"}]}